// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/cltBDs try moebius map by triangle pair, 2023 by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mltfWX learning moebius transformation

// Trying to calculate the Möbius Transformation that maps one triangle onto another.
// Using this transformation because it maps generalized circles to generalized circles.
// Thanks to mla for fixing missing complex multiplication!

// TODO: cleanup & movement.

// see e.g.
// https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moebius_transformation
// https://delta.cs.cinvestav.mx/~mcintosh/comun/complex/node10.html
